Description
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

MAVLink Companion Log Service automatically archives ArduPilot DataFlash logs
from a flight controller to a companion computer after every flight, verifies
each download, and erases the flight controller logs only after all logs in a
cycle are durably stored. The service communicates exclusively over MAVLink.

